<text top="404" left="128" width="388" height="11" font="6"><b>Efforts by the Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human  </b></text>
<text top="417" left="128" width="368" height="11" font="6"><b>Rights for universal ratification of the International Convention on the  </b></text>
<text top="431" left="128" width="380" height="11" font="6"><b>                    Elimination of All Forms of Racial Discrimination                     </b></text>
<text top="457" left="260" width="121" height="11" font="6"><b>Note by the Secretariat </b></text>
<text top="483" left="85" width="3" height="11" font="0"> </text>
<text top="483" left="113" width="418" height="11" font="0">In its decision 2/102, the Human Rights Council requested the High Commissioner for </text>
<text top="496" left="85" width="469" height="11" font="0">Human Rights to “continue with the fulfilment of [her] activities, in accordance with all previous </text>
<text top="510" left="85" width="456" height="11" font="0">decisions adopted by the Commission on Human Rights and to update the relevant reports and </text>
<text top="524" left="85" width="45" height="11" font="0">studies”. </text>
<text top="550" left="85" width="3" height="11" font="0"> </text>
<text top="550" left="113" width="402" height="11" font="0">The Secretariat informs the Human Rights Council that an update to the note of the </text>
<text top="564" left="85" width="458" height="11" font="0">Secretariat submitted to the Council at its fourth session (A/HRC/4/51), outlining the efforts of </text>
<text top="577" left="85" width="470" height="11" font="0">the Office of the High Commissioner for Human Rights to encourage the universal ratification of </text>
<text top="591" left="85" width="459" height="11" font="0">the International Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Racial Discrimination, will be </text>
<text top="605" left="85" width="235" height="11" font="0">submitted for consideration at its eighth session. </text>
